window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - LOSS OF LIMBS 重病保障索償表格 － 斷肢 Policy No. 保單編號： PART", "f": "C31.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE - LOSS OF LIMBS 重病保障索償表格 － 斷肢 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which the patient first consulted you related to the condition (Loss of Limbs). 病人就是項疾病（斷肢）首次向閣下求診的日期（DD日/ MM月/YY年）。 b) What were the symptoms? 病人之病徵？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing these symptoms before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有此病徵多久？ d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果?（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient’s family history which would have increased the risk of the disease specified above? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上上述疾病機 會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. What is/are the underlying cause(s) of the loss of limbs? 什麼原因引致病人的斷肢？ 11. a) Where is the site of the severance? 何處肢體被切斷？ b) Is the severance above the wrist or the ankle? 被切斷的部分是否手腕或腳踝以上？ Yes, please provide details: 有，請詳述： No 沒有 12. Is the severance of limb(s) total and irreversible? (Please enclose copies of all supportive reports and relevant medical reports that are available). 病人的肢體截斷是否完全且不可逆轉？ （請提供有關檢驗報告及醫療報告副本） Yes, please provide details: 有，請詳述： No 不是 Test Date (DD/MM/YY) 檢驗日期(日/月/年) Test Item 檢驗項目 Result / Diagnosis 結果/診斷 13. Is there any other surgery/treatment help to improve the patient’s condition? 有否手術或治療可改善病人的情況？ Yes, please provide details: 有，請詳述： 14. What is the prognosis of the patient? 病人現時進展及狀況？ No 沒有 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C31 (11/2025) 1 of 2 Policy No. 保單編號： 15. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 16. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C31 (11/2025) 2 of 2"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE MAJOR BURN/FACIAL BURNS DUE TO ACCIDENT/ LESS SEVER", "f": "C37.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE MAJOR BURN/FACIAL BURNS DUE TO ACCIDENT/ LESS SEVERE BURNS TO BODY DUE TO ACCIDENT 重病保障索償表格 － 嚴重灼傷/意外引致的 面部灼傷/意外引致的次級嚴重身體灼傷 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which the patient first consulted you related to the condition (Major Burn / Facial Burns Due To Accident / Less Severe Burns To Body Due To Accident). 病人就是項疾病（嚴重灼傷/意外引致的面部灼傷/意外引致的次級嚴重身體灼傷）首次向閣下求診的日期（DD日/ MM月/YY年）。 b) What were the symptoms? 病人之病徵？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing these symptoms before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有此病徵多久？ d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果?（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient’s family history which would have increased the risk of the disease specified above? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上上述疾病機 會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the extent of the major burns. 請描述該燒傷之狀況。 i) Please describe the exact area(s) of the burns, e.g face, body, hand, foot, etc. 請描述該燒傷之正確位置，如臉部、身體、手部、腳部等。 ii) Date of f Accident 意外日期： ( / / ) DD/MM/YYYY 日/月/年 iii) Is the burns considered as Third Degree Burns (full thickness skin destruction)? 該燒傷之程度是否屬於第三級燒傷(皮膚全層燒傷)？ Yes 是 No 否 If so, please describe (in percentages): 如“是”，請列出燒傷之程度(百分比)： a) the total body area reaching third degree burns 達三級燒傷的身體總面積： b) the total area of the face alone reaching third degree burns 達三級燒傷的臉部總面積： 11. What was the cause of the burns? 該燒傷是因何引致？ 12. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C37 (11/2025) 1 of 2 Policy No. 保單編號： 13. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C37 (11/2025) 2 of 2"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE FULMINANT VIRAL HEPATITIS/ HEPATITIS WITH CIRRHOSIS", "f": "C43.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE FULMINANT VIRAL HEPATITIS/ HEPATITIS WITH CIRRHOSIS 重病保障索償表格 － 暴發性病毒性肝炎/ 肝炎連肝硬化 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which the patient first consulted you related to the condition (Fulminant Viral Hepatitis / Hepatitis With Cirrhosis). 病人就是項疾病（暴發性病毒性肝炎/ 肝炎連肝硬化）首次向閣下求診的日期（DD日/ MM月/YY年）。 b) What were the symptoms? 病人之病徵？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing these symptoms before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有此病徵多久？ d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient’s family history which would have increased the risk of the disease specified above? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上上述疾病機 會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please complete this section for Fulminant Viral Hepatitis Disease. 暴發性病毒性肝炎，請填寫此部份。 i. Was there a rapidly decreasing liver size? 肝臟有沒有急劇縮小？ Yes 是 No 沒有 ii. Was there a necrosis involving entire lobules, leaving only a collapsed reticular framework of the liver? 肝臟的小葉是否完全壞死，只剩下倒塌的支架結構？ Yes 是 No 沒有 iii. Was there a rapid degeneration of liver function? 肝臟功能測試有沒有急劇退化？ Yes 是 No 沒有 iv. Was there a rapid deterioration of liver enzymes? 肝酶有沒有急劇惡化？ Yes 是 No 沒有 v. Was there any deepening jaundice? 有沒有嚴重及持續加深之黃疸？ Yes 是 No 沒有 vi. Was Hepatic Encephalopathy resulted? 有沒有引致肝性腦病？ Yes 是 No 沒有 11. Please complete this section for Hepatitis with Cirrhosis. 肝炎連肝硬化，請填此部份。 i. Was Inflammation of Liver leading to Cirrhosis resulted? 有沒有引致肝臟發炎並發展成肝硬化？ Yes 是 No 沒有 If “yes”, has liver biopsy done to confirm the diagnosis? 如“有”，有沒有以肝活組織檢查術確診？ Yes 是 No 沒有 What is the biopsy result according to Metavir grading or Knodell fibrosis score? 根據Metavir分級表或Knodell肝纖維化標準，受保人的肝活組織檢查結果為何？ (Please provide copy of biopsy report for reference. 請提供肝活組織檢查報告以供參考。) a. Metavir Grading: Histological Stage Metavir 分級表:屬 階段 b. Knodell fibrosis score: Knodell肝纖維化標準: ii. Was the diagnosis of liver cirrhosis confirmed by a gastroenterologist? 肝硬化是否由腸胃專科醫生確定？ Yes 是 No 否 Please give the Name and Address of the gastroenterologist if it is not the undersigned. 若非由填寫此表格之醫生確認，請提供腸胃專科醫生之姓名及地址。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C43 (11/2025) 1 of 2 12. What is the current condition of the Insured and what is the prognosis? 受保人之現今病況及病情進展。 Policy No. 保單編號： 13. Is the liver disease / disorder related to alcohol and/or drug abuse? If yes, please give details. 肝臟疾病/紊亂是否與酒精及/或濫用藥物有關? 如是，請提供詳情。 14. Please enclose copies of all reports including liver biopsy, liver function tests, ultrasound, MRI and other imaging studies, laboratory evidence, etc. and any relevant hospital reports that are available. 請提供所有報告包括肝活組織檢查、肝功化驗、超聲波、電腦掃描及其他影像報告,或任何有關的醫院報告。 15. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C43 (11/2025) 2 of 2"});
