window.__KB.push({"t": "LETTER OF REQUEST AND INDEMNITY (Early Release of Medical Cards / Panel Service)", "f": "團體保險醫療卡同意書.pdf", "s": "LETTER OF REQUEST AND INDEMNITY (Early Release of Medical Cards / Panel Service) To: Manulife (International) Limited (“Manulife”) Policy No. : (the “Policy”) Policyholder Name : I understand and acknowledge that Manulife will not release the medical cards or renew the panel service (as the case may be) to the above Policyholder and its insured members unless and until payment of the premium required to effect the Policy or renewal of the Policy (as the case may be) has been made (the “Standard Procedure”). Notwithstanding the Standard Procedure, I hereby request that Manulife releases the medical cards or renew the panel service (as the case may be) to the Policyholder and its insured members before payment of the aforesaid premium is made (the \"Request\"). In consideration of Manulife complying with my Request, I agree to indemnify Manulife and hold Manulife harmless against all loss and expenses and damages suffered or incurred by Manulife as a direct or indirect result of Manulife complying with the Request. Please arrange to send the medical cards (if any) to me for distributing to the Policyholder / its insured members; or Please arrange to deliver the medical cards (if any) to the Policyholder directly. ✔ (In the absence of in any box above, the medical cards shall be delivered to the agent for distributing to the Policyholder / its insured members) For renewal Policy, I understand that the above requested medical cards / panel service will only be released in around 4 working days upon receipt by Manulife of this Letter of Request and Indemnity and all required documents (i.e. renewal confirmation / signed proposal) and the completion of the benefit changes (if any). As such, please be confirmed that this undertaking has been submitted together with the renewal confirmation / signed proposal to Manulife for processing. Agent Name: Agent Code: Date: Version: 08/2017"});
